name: Aqua Quartz Collar
description: Aqua Quartz Collar Necklace Highly polished, translucent aqua quartz crystal ovals accented by tiny silver beads. Finished with a lobster clasp. Sizing: Necklace is 16" long, designed to lay across the collar bone.

name: Bone Spike Necklace
description: Bone Fringe Bolo Necklace Smoothly polished bone spikes dangle from a flat cable steel chain with an antiqued brass finish. Sizing: Necklace is 18 inches long with 5 and 6 inch drop chains. Closes with a lobster clasp and an extender chain of 1.5 inches. Bone spikes range from 1-2 inches depending on natural variations.

name: Jasper Tiered Necklace
description: Jasper Tiered Necklace A multi-strand necklace consisting of 5 layers of dark green natural Kambaba Jasper beads. The clasp is a sliding lock, which is incredibly secure and prevents the strands from tangling. This design is created using the Japanese pearl knotting technique, a traditional method employed by professional jewelers to reduce friction between beads and help prevent the threads from fraying. Sizing: The individual strands measure 14, 16, 18, 24, and 30 inches long.

name: Ammonite Fossil Pendant
description: Ammonite Fossil Pendant An authentic ammonite fossil fashioned into a pendant, suspended from an antiqued silver cable chain finished with a lobster clasp. Sizing: Chain measures 18 inches long. Pendant is approximately 1.5 inches in diameter, but individual sizes will vary slightly.
